metadata.name: Wheel of Fortune
metadata.description:
One of my original mobile photographs showcases the power and strength of the Ain Dubai from underneath the supporting structure.

The curves and lines in the architecture of this build are breathtaking up close. Watching the wheel turn from the ground and actually seeing the movements in action is simply amazing.

The Ain Dubai is currently the World's Highest Observation Wheel. It is a superb facility and the sheer size of the project is awe-inspiring.
